# One line-ending story on every platform. The generated JSON artifacts embed
# newline-normalized byte counts and the CI determinism gate diffs regenerated files
# against the committed ones — CRLF-smudged checkouts (Windows autocrlf) broke both.
* text=auto
*.rs text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf
*.svg text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.toml text eol=lf
*.ps1 text eol=lf

*.wasm binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ppm binary
*.bin binary
